WEBVTT

00:04.199 --> 00:11.447
The Colored Man's Lament, Abe Melton, Alphabet, March 4, 1939.

00:11.527 --> 00:32.991
Oh, just a little while to stay here, just a little while to wait, just a little more of labor, creeping to the pearly gates.

00:33.511 --> 00:42.013
Oh, just a little while to stay, just a little while to roam.

00:42.755 --> 00:53.443
Just a little more of trouble, and then we'll all go home.

